    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>The memorial event, which will give people the opportunity to remember the six million Jews that were persecuted and murdered by the Nazi regime and its collaborators, as well as other instances of genocide, will be held at Queen Margaret University (QMU) on the 29th January. The theme of this year’s memorial day at QMU is ‘How can life go on?’</p>]]></Value>
